title: The End Game
description: We went through all that just to be strangers again.Carter Flynn might love me.But I'm done with him.He may well be the sexiest man I've ever been with, but he has a dark side.It's a hard decision, but I say this relationship is over.Carter begs to differ.I just embrace my new life in New York as a dancer.It goes smoothly until Carter sees me walking home one morning...after I've been out all night at the club with a new man.If we have a happily ever after coming to us, I sure can't see it.
author: Mickey Miller
